# Cleave project context

- BAU iterative development. Entry point: [cleave.py](cleave.py) (four libprojectM layers, 1280x720 / 30 fps default, stem PCM). Black-key stack in [cleave/gl_compositor.py](cleave/gl_compositor.py). Live tuning overlay: [cleave/viz_tuning_overlay.py](cleave/viz_tuning_overlay.py), [cleave/viz_tuning_controls.py](cleave/viz_tuning_controls.py). Cleave effects: [cleave/effects/](cleave/effects/). Config: [cleave.config.yaml](cleave.config.yaml); snapshots in [saved-cleave-configs/](saved-cleave-configs/) via [cleave/config_snapshot.py](cleave/config_snapshot.py).
- Must-do list: [docs/todos.md](docs/todos.md). Aspirational: [docs/roadmap.md](docs/roadmap.md).
- See [README.md](README.md) for usage.
- Stem layout: `stems/<trackname>/` with four wavs plus `signals.json`. CLI: `python -m cleave separate|analyse`; visualizer: `python cleave.py`.
- Overlay layout and typography: [.cursor/rules/live-tuning-ui.mdc](.cursor/rules/live-tuning-ui.mdc).
